---

# 📌 Related Components

This dashboard forms part of an end-to-end cloud analytics pipeline consisting of:

- **Amazon S3** – Raw data storage
- **Snowflake** – Cloud data warehouse and transformation
- **Snowflake SQL** – Data preparation and enrichment
- **Power BI** – Business Intelligence reporting
- **Power BI Service** – Cloud-based report publishing
